metadata.name: MPM1
metadata.description:
Hid within so many
sounds and words
voices needing to be heard
Ears to hear eyes to see
what all is in this he-art
Awaiting to be known
Seen and heard
understood and comprehending
Soul touching soul
This the true reach
Resonance of vision
Sounds in colors
Calling out to all
Seeing is hearing .
Listen and see
Open those doors with the
Sacred heart key attuned
Heart strings plucking
Open and ready for all
applauding the journey
ATO
